{
  "id": "RAW_bb13ecdb",
  "title": "刚刚，这个热门前端框架被大厂收购!",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU2MTIyNDUwMA==&mid=2247536584&idx=1&sn=e2c2c84a10fb05d99a846989a8743e05",
  "date": "2026-01-16 16:39:00",
  "author": "前端充电宝",
  "siteName": "前端充电宝",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=00825819&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FEO58xpw5UMM0J3epAUqA7unApjRKE5FHtiaLiaHMxvtrSre8gYKow4S25MK0GutYBmoz6T31Ke3dicIuZCGnkPzQA%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <div data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"word-wrap:break-word;overflow:hidden;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'SF Pro Text', 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif;\">\n    <div style=\"height: auto;\">\n     <div>\n      <p class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\"><mp-common-profile class=\"js_uneditable custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-nickname=\"前端充电宝\" data-alias=\"FE-Charge\" data-from=\"0\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/EO58xpw5UMNJLOYUj7Uv3TSiaqDldeaxxhCosR00yDKGR9lvI4y9NOfG7ADJHfKEsKuVAFWgDPqLN5afgZGkbZg/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-signature=\"聚焦前端开发，探索AI新浪潮：宝藏工具×前沿动态×实战技巧，解锁前端新可能！\" data-id=\"MzU2MTIyNDUwMA==\" data-is_biz_ban=\"0\" data-service_type=\"1\" data-verify_status=\"0\"></mp-common-profile></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">刚刚，Cloudflare 宣布：</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">Astro 核心团队正式加入 Cloudflare</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">对，就是那个 2025 年崩了 5 次的 Cloudflare，这是一家提供</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">全球边缘网络服务</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">的公司，帮网站和应用实现</span><strong style=\"overflow:hidden;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;line-height:2;overflow-wrap:break-word;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">加速访问、安全防护和更稳定的在线运行</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。Cloudflare 大约</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">覆盖了全球 20% 的网站和互联网请求流量，在使用 CDN/反向代理的网站中拥有约 80% 以上的市场渗透率。</span></strong></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果你平时关注前端生态，对这个名字大概率不陌生。更准确地说——</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">Astro 是那种刚开源就爆火的项目</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">2021 年 Astro 正式开源时，技术社区几乎是集体讨论。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">原因也很简单：</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">它做了一件很多前端早就想做、但一直没被真正落地的事——尽量不往浏览器里塞 JavaScript。</span></strong></p>\n      <h2 style=\"margin-top: 16px;line-height: 1.25;display: table;padding: 0.4em 1.4em;margin: 3em auto 1.5em;color: #fff;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1677ff, #05d4cd);font-size: 1.3em;font-weight: 600;text-align: center;border-radius: 8px 24px 8px 24px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;\"><span leaf=\"\">Astro 到底是什么？</span></h2>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">一句话概括：</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">Astro 是一个“默认不发 JS”的前端框架。</span></strong></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">它主打&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">HTML First + Islands 架构</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：</span></p>\n      <div style=\"margin: 16px 0;background: rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.02);padding: 12px;border-radius: 8px 16px 8px 16px;\">\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">页面默认输出纯 HTML</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">只有真正需要交互的部分才加载 JS</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 0;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">React / Vue / Svelte 可以混着用，但不是前提条件</span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这套思路，在当时几乎是对「一切皆 SPA」的正面挑战。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">也正因为如此，Astro 刚开源那会儿，才会在技术社区引发这么大的讨论声量。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">很多前端第一次用 Astro 的反应都很一致：</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">原来页面，真的可以不用那么重。</span></p>\n      <h2 style=\"margin-top: 16px;line-height: 1.25;display: table;padding: 0.4em 1.4em;margin: 3em auto 1.5em;color: #fff;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1677ff, #05d4cd);font-size: 1.3em;font-weight: 600;text-align: center;border-radius: 8px 24px 8px 24px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;\"><span leaf=\"\">不只是“理念火”，生态也真的跑起来了</span></h2>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">更重要的是，</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">Astro 并没有停留在“概念正确”阶段。</span></strong></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">经过这几年的发展，它已经形成了一套</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">相当完整的生态</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：</span></p>\n      <div style=\"margin: 16px 0;background: rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.02);padding: 12px;border-radius: 8px 16px 8px 16px;\">\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">官方集成体系，覆盖 **React、Vue、Svelte、Solid **等主流框架</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">成熟的&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">内容体系</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：Markdown / MDX / Content Collections</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">完整的渲染能力：</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">SSG + SSR + Edge SSR</span></strong></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">部署生态非常广：</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">Cloudflare Pages、Netlify、Vercel、Node、Deno</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;都是一等公民</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 0;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">周边工具也逐渐完善：图片优化、国际化、搜索、文档站模板一应俱全</span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">到今天，Astro 已经不再是“玩票型新框架”，而是一个</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">可以稳定承载文档站、官网、博客、内容平台的成熟方案</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n      <h2 style=\"margin-top: 16px;line-height: 1.25;display: table;padding: 0.4em 1.4em;margin: 3em auto 1.5em;color: #fff;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1677ff, #05d4cd);font-size: 1.3em;font-weight: 600;text-align: center;border-radius: 8px 24px 8px 24px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;\"><span leaf=\"\">那 Cloudflare 为什么要收购 Astro？</span></h2>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这一步，其实非常 Cloudflare。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这几年 Cloudflare 的路线已经非常清晰：</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">从 CDN → Edge 平台 → 开发者基础设施。</span></strong></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">有 Workers（计算）、Pages（部署）、D1 / KV / R2（存储），而 Astro，正好补上了“内容层”的最后一块拼图。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Cloudflare 团队也明确提到：他们看重的不是 Astro 属不属于 Cloudflare，而是&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">Astro 所代表的那种“更快、更轻、更贴近 Web 本质的构建方式</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n      <h2 style=\"margin-top: 16px;line-height: 1.25;display: table;padding: 0.4em 1.4em;margin: 3em auto 1.5em;color: #fff;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1677ff, #05d4cd);font-size: 1.3em;font-weight: 600;text-align: center;border-radius: 8px 24px 8px 24px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;\"><span leaf=\"\">会不会“收购后变味”？</span></h2>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这是大家最关心的问题。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">目前官方给出的信号很明确：</span></p>\n      <div style=\"margin: 16px 0;background: rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.02);padding: 12px;border-radius: 8px 16px 8px 16px;\">\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">Astro 继续&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">MIT 协议开源</span></strong></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">不会变成 Cloudflare 私有框架</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 0;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">原班团队继续负责 Astro 的演进</span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这从目前释放的信息来看，这更像是一次</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">大厂为成熟开源项目提供长期保障的典型案例</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n      <h2 style=\"margin-top: 16px;line-height: 1.25;display: table;padding: 0.4em 1.4em;margin: 3em auto 1.5em;color: #fff;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1677ff, #05d4cd);font-size: 1.3em;font-weight: 600;text-align: center;border-radius: 8px 24px 8px 24px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;\"><span leaf=\"\">一个更大的信号</span></h2>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">我反而觉得，这次事件背后真正值得关注的是：</span></p>\n      <blockquote style=\"margin-top: 16px;font-style: italic;margin: 20px 0;padding: 12px 20px;background: rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.04);border-left: 4px solid #0066ff;border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;\">\n       <p style=\"margin: 0;color: #4e5969;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">前端，并不一定非要越来越重。</span></strong></p>\n      </blockquote>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在大家卷 SSR、卷 RSC、卷全栈的时候，Astro 用这几年的发展证明了一件事：</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">内容型网站，有一条已经被验证、而且足够成熟的技术路线。</span></strong></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">而 Cloudflare 选择在这个时间点站到 Astro 身后，本身就是一种态度。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果你还没认真用过 Astro，现在再回头看它，可能正好是一个重新评估的节点。</span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文报道了 Cloudflare 收购热门前端框架 Astro 的消息，并深入分析了 Astro 的核心技术理念、生态成熟度以及此次收购对前端技术发展和 Cloudflare 战略布局的深远意义。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文报道了 Cloudflare 收购热门前端框架 Astro 的消息，并深入分析了 Astro 的核心技术理念、生态成熟度以及此次收购对前端技术发展和 Cloudflare 战略布局的深远意义。",
  "summary": "Cloudflare 正式宣布收购新兴前端框架 Astro 的核心团队，并将其纳入 Cloudflare 生态。文章首先介绍了 Cloudflare 及其在全球边缘网络服务领域的领导地位，随后详细阐述了 Astro 框架的独特之处，即其“默认不发 JS”的理念、HTML First 和 Islands 架构，旨在构建更轻量、更快的网站。Astro 经过几年的发展，已形成了涵盖主流框架集成、内容体系、渲染能力及广泛部署生态的成熟体系，证明了其不仅仅是“概念正确”，而是可投入生产的解决方案。文章进一步分析了 Cloudflare 收购 Astro 的战略意图，指出这补齐了 Cloudflare 从 CDN 到边缘开发者基础设施转型的“内容层”拼图，体现了其对“更快、更轻、更贴近 Web 本质”构建方式的认可。最后，文章探讨了社区对“收购后变味”的担忧，并指出官方承诺 Astro 将继续开源并由原团队负责演进，更像是一次大厂为开源项目提供长期保障的案例，并借此强调前端发展并非必然走向“越来越重”的趋势。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Cloudflare 收购 Astro 核心团队，旨在补齐其开发者基础设施的内容层版图。",
      "explanation": "Cloudflare 将 Astro 视为其从 CDN 转型为边缘计算平台的关键一环，Astro 的轻量化和高性能特性与 Cloudflare 的战略方向高度契合，从而完善了其在 Workers、Pages 和存储服务之外的内容构建能力。"
